NK103(pe)019:1: // ra t+na pra b+h+aa ti sma ///
NK103(pe)019:6: rna brgyud rin po che yis snying po'i don gsal bar byed pas 'od ces bya ba /
NK103(pe)019:7: rang 'od thugs dam gyi lhar rang snang ba'i dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK103(pe)019:8: gnas lugs lhun grub gsum du gsal bas kun khyab
NK103(pe)019:9: mi 'byed pa'i thugs rje rang rig pa nyid la
NK103(pe)019:10: rang chas su gnas pa'i dpal te sku gsum rang
NK103(pe)019:11: rig pa pad+ma gsum po nyid ldan pa de la
NK103(pe)019:12: dga' ba'am dang ba'i tshul gyis 'dud cing phyag 'tshal
NK103(pe)019:13: lo // rgyal ba'i thugs garje'i byin gyis brlabs ba'i rna brgyud kyi gdams pa ni /
NK103(pe)019:14: 'phags pa'i sku dang byin rlabs kyis //
NK103(pe)019:15: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing+ha nyid la rang shar ba ni
NK103(pe)019:16: nyi ma lta bur gsal bas gzhan gyi sems nyid
NK103(pe)019:17: kyang gsal bar byed pa'i gdams ngag rin chen snang
NK103(pe)019:18: ba 'od 'di // grangs mtha' chayas pa'i 'gro ba'i ris thams cad la'ang //
NK103(pe)019:19: dbyer med kyi tshul gyis ldan mod gyis kyang //
NK103(pe)019:20: bdag 'dzin log pa'i sems tshogs brgyad kyis dkrugs pas
NK103(pe)019:21: yod kyang mi gsal ba ni sa 'og gi gter
NK103(pe)019:22: gyi bum pa yod kyang mi gsal ba ji bzhin
NK103(pe)019:23: pas // gdams ngag rin chen snang ba 'od 'dis rang 'bar du ston pa yin //
NK103(pe)019:24: 'gro khaba'i bla ma thub pa'i dbang po yun mi ring ba zhig bzhugs nas 'das par gyur kyang //
NK103(pe)019:25: gang la bzhag na 'gro ngaba ma rig pa'i mun pa la gnas pa rnams kyi nang nas //
NK103(pe)019:26: rnal ma'i don la mos pa'i rnal 'byor pa shes rab kyi mig med pa pa rnams la //
NK103(pe)019:27: snying 1po rnal ma'i don gsal ba 'od kyi don
NK103(pe)019:28: du rna brgyud kyi man ngag 'di bzhag par bya'o
NK103(pe)019:29: // mtsho chen po'i gting kagser du yod pa ltar
NK103(pe)019:30: mi brjod bya gsal ba'i byang chub kyi sems rin
NK103(pe)019:31: // po che // snying po rnal ma rtogs pa'i
NK103(pe)019:32: skal caldan rnal 'byor 'dir mos 'jug 'brel pa gis
NK103(pe)019:33: // po che // // khams gsum gyi sems dang
NK103(pe)019:34: sems byung sgro btags kyi rtog pa med dgos pa
NK103(pe)019:35: yul med rang gsal du mthong ba'i lam mngon sum
NK103(pe)019:36: du rtogs pa dang gzod lam rim pas jabgrod med
NK103(pe)019:37: de mthar thug gi 'bras nying dgos bur rang la
NK103(pe)019:39: shes pa gsum gyis ma gos pas pad+ma kadbang po
NK103(pe)019:40: sprul gsang ba'i chos snying longs gsum gyi dkyil 'khor
NK103(pe)019:41: rtogs nas // bde gshegs gsum gyi skur ldan pa
NK103(pe)019:42: ni rnam grol gyi 'bras bu rang bzhag tu gnas
NK103(pe)019:43: pa yin te gzhi phyi mo nas ma g.yos par
NK103(pe)019:44: 'bras bu rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par bya'o //
NK103(pe)019:45: chos nyid sku la dus gsum du 'gyur ba med de //
NK103(pe)019:46: rang rig pa rtsol ba med pa bde ba chen
NK103(pe)019:47: po'i ngang du gnas pas rgyu yis bskyed pa la
NK103(pe)019:48: mi gnas par sgrib byed dang bral bar mthar thug
NK103(pe)019:49: pa ni // theg chen gyi 'bras bu kun rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu yin no //
NK103(pe)019:50: don de gang gis shes par 'gyur na bla na rin chen gyi gsung gis shes par 'gyur te //
NK103(pe)019:51: gang shes par 'gyur na gsal byed gdams ngag de'i
NK103(pe)019:52: brjod bya snying po'i yin lugs kyi don de shes
NK103(pe)019:53: so // theg pa kun gyis brjod par bya ba
NK103(pe)019:54: ni sems kyi dbyings de la theg pa rang rang
NK103(pe)019:55: mos pa'i shes pas mu bzhi so sor rtogs //
NK103(pe)019:56: lam gyi bgrod pa'i rtsol bas 'bras bu tshol //
NK103(pe)019:57: rang rang mos pa'am bsam pa'i sa la gnas te //
NK103(pe)019:58: thob par smon pa'i 'dod pas 'bras bu gzhan nas re ba yid la 'jog /
NK103(pe)019:59: snying po rnal ma'i lam la 'bras bu smon pa'i 'dod pa bral te re ba /
NK103(pe)019:60: yid la mi byed de 'bras bu rang bzhin kun khyab tu gnas pa la rtogs pa /
NK103(pe)019:61: rig pa'i gzer gyis don las 'da' ba med pas
NK103(pe)019:62: bsgom du med de don la rtsol ba'i bya ba
NK103(pe)019:63: bral lo // lta ba mthong du med pa'i snying po ni //
NK103(pe)019:64: rang sor bzhag pa'i sems kyi rig pas shes //
NK103(pe)019:65: rdo rje theg pa'i bka' ni rtogs par byed pa'i tshig gi lam //
NK103(pe)019:66: rtogs par byed pa'i sgra la don du gnyer ba'i
NK103(pe)019:67: sems kyis tshul bzang po'i rtsol ba la rnal 'byor
NK103(pe)019:69: brda sprod par byed pa'i don dang phrad par gyur nas //
NK103(pe)019:70: brjod par bya ba'i rang bzhin snying po'i don shes par bya //
NK103(pe)019:71: rgyal ba'i sku gsum dgongs pa nyid rig pa'i thabs ni //
NK103(pe)019:72: thug phrad gsum gyi byed pa'i rin po che 'od kyis mthong //
NK103(pe)019:73: thug phrad gsum gyis lhun grub gsum gyi 'od gsal ba ni gzhi yi lam //
NK103(pe)019:74: gsal bya gsal byed dang bral ba'i ngang nyid la gnas //
NK103(pe)019:75: lam thug phrad gsum gyis lam gyi 'bras bu sku gsum mthong //
NK103(pe)019:76: 'bras bu sku gsum dgongs pa'i rgyal ba'i thugs po //
NK103(pe)019:77: de ni rtog pas bsam du med de rang bzhag rig pa'i ngang ngo //
NK103(pe)019:78: bde chen mi rtog yid rgyu ba'i rnam rtog bral te //
NK103(pe)019:79: yid la mi byed kyang rang 'od kyi snang ba dag /
NK103(pe)019:80: rig pa ma bkag pas ye shes su gsal lo //
NK103(pe)019:81: dbang po lnga'i pad+ma bzhi cha rig pa rang gsal ni rgyal ba'i thugs so //
NK103(pe)019:82: de ni 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gyis gnas //
NK103(pe)019:83: yul lnga mthong ba yin don las log pa rang rig pa las gzhan du 'dod kyang /
NK103(pe)019:84: sprul sku dang po skyes la mi rtog pa ni yul snang nyid las gzhan las 'byung ba min //
NK103(pe)019:85: de'i bskyang thabs kun bzang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa de nyid //
NK103(pe)019:86: snang ba'i tshul gyis ngos gzung ba byas la zin
NK103(pe)019:87: pa'i don de dran pa'i tshul gyis nyams su blang
NK103(pe)019:88: // skye dus yul lnga la rnam shes lnga 'phen pa skad cig dang po'i dus na skye'o //
NK103(pe)019:89: gdams ngag rin chen yul lnga /
NK103(pe)019:93: thabs kyi bye brag brtag thabs ldog tshul log pa'i tshad rnams shes par gyur na //
NK103(pe)019:95: rtog dpyod tha snyad 'dogs pa'i thog ma'i dbang po'i pad+ma ji bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:96: bkra gsal gzugs la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lnga yis ye shes 'phro ba'i rtogs pa /
NK103(pe)019:97: de dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa ni rgyal ba'i gral du gnas so //
NK103(pe)019:98: rang gnas kyi thugs rje bzhi cha rang gsal 'gro
NK103(pe)019:99: ba kun la ldan kyang gsum ldan 'khor ba'i rnyog
NK103(pe)019:100: pas bslad kyang dwangs ma chos nyid ni dus gsum
NK103(pe)019:102: gsang ba'i pad+ma sngags kyi sems rtsol bral zin dang
NK103(pe)019:103: ma zin par de yid rtog pa dang dpyod pa
NK103(pe)019:104: dang bral ba'i dus na ngo shes //
NK103(pe)019:105: sngar gyi rtog dpyod kyi bya ba btang phyis kyi
NK103(pe)019:106: bya ba bzhag bar pa ni rang bzhin gyis bya
NK103(pe)019:107: ba dang bral bas 'khor ba rnam par mi sems
NK103(pe)019:108: te // mya ngan 'das pa'i rgyu ba rnam rtog dang 'ang bral //
NK103(pe)019:109: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas chos sku dgongs pa bya ba med pa la //
NK103(pe)019:110: dus gsum du ma yengs par srog ting nge 'dzin tu sems shig /
NK103(pe)019:111: de la blang dor mi mnga' lta ba med de de ka rang bzhin rgyal ba'i lta ba yin //
NK103(pe)019:112: blos ched du mi rtsol ba ni dbu ma drang po'i lam //
NK103(pe)019:113: gang gis kyang ma bcos pa rgyal ba'i thugs kyi lam ga yin no //
NK103(pe)019:114: khasnying gi pad+ma rin po che //
NK103(pe)019:115: nya'od gsal rig pa'i dkyil 'khor ye shes lnga ru //
NK103(pe)019:116: 1chags pa la sogs pa nyon mongs lnga //
NK103(pe)019:117: mthar thug tha ma'i dus na mthong //
NK103(pe)019:118: nyon mongs pa gang skyes dus na de'i yul la
NK103(pe)019:119: mi dpyad de nyon mongs pa ched du mi dgag
NK103(pe)019:120: par de'i ngo bo rang gsal nyid la gzhag cago
NK103(pe)019:121: // nga gsang ba'i pad+ma ni chos kyi sku //
NK103(pe)019:122: ma bcos rang gsal yid spros pa'i gzung 'dzin dang bral ba dang //
NK103(pe)019:123: rdzogs pa'i longs spyod nyon mongs rang gsal bde ba chen po'i sku dang //
NK103(pe)019:124: nyasprul sku yul lnga gang snang la'ang ngos gzung med
NK103(pe)019:125: pa dang gsum dbyer med par rang rig pa byang
NK103(pe)019:126: chub kyi sems gcig la gnas so //
NK103(pe)019:127: yul du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang bral ba'i mngon sum pa //
NK103(pe)019:128: zhen chags dang bral ba'i bde ba che //
NK103(pe)019:129: brjod pa'i tha snyad lta ba dang bral ba'i thabs kyis mtshon //
NK103(pe)019:130: rtsol dang bral ba'i spyod pas dang du blang //
NK103(pe)019:131: phar spro ba dang tshur bsdu sgom pa med pa'i dgongs pas gnas //
NK103(pe)019:132: snang ba rgya mtsho chen po mi g.yo ba bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:133: rang bzhag rig pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:134: de'i yon tan sna tshogs 'char ba ni nam mkha'i ngang la kun 'char ba bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:135: kadus kha gsum 'gyur med kun tu bzang po'i ngang
NK103(pe)019:136: la sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med pas 'khor
NK103(pe)019:137: ba'i dus nyid na rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK103(pe)019:138: ste dper na rin chen dag pa ji bzhin no
NK103(pe)019:139: // 'khrul pa ji ltar bcos kyang yin lugs la 'gyur ba med de //
NK103(pe)019:140: rang bzhin chos nyid ngo bo la ci'i ngo bor
NK103(pe)019:141: kyang ma grub pas sgro 1'dogs dang skur 'debs 11spros
NK103(pe)019:143: nga bdag tu 'dzin pa'i shes pa log pas rgyun
NK103(pe)019:144: du bslad pas rang byung rig pa'i don ma rtogs
NK103(pe)019:145: // rang byung kun mkhyen rig pa'i thugs de ni
NK103(pe)019:146: 'gyur ba med par 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin
NK103(pe)019:147: // gyis gnas // nam mkha' gdod nas gnas pa
NK103(pe)019:148: dang 'dra bar rang byung ye shes lhun gyis grub
NK103(pe)019:149: // gyis gnas // // logs nas bsgrub tu med pa'i dngos grub chen po la //
NK103(pe)019:150: bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig rang bzhag ste //
NK103(pe)019:151: spros pa'i mtha' med de la ltos pa'i dbus med
NK103(pe)019:152: de rig par gsal ba de nyid rgyal ba kun
NK103(pe)019:154: sems can kun gyi rang bzhin yin no //
NK103(pe)019:155: ye shes rig pas don de rtogs par gyur nas //
NK103(pe)019:156: thugs rje mdzad pa'i lam yang 'gro ba la ston //
NK103(pe)019:157: sems kyi 'bras bu rang bzhag du gnas na 'byung ba la //
NK103(pe)019:158: 'dod pa'i rtsol bas gzhan nas 'grub par mi byed do //
NK103(pe)019:159: jabyang cachub sems kyi lam chen ni //
NK103(pe)019:160: rnam dag ye shes dgongs pa'i lam ste //
NK103(pe)019:161: thun mong du 'gro ba yongs kyi sems kyi chos
NK103(pe)019:162: nyid la gnas pas dus gsum sangs rgyas kyang sems
NK103(pe)019:163: las byung // rtsol bas bgrod du med pa rang rig ye shes kyi lam //
NK103(pe)019:164: rang rang gi 'dod pas bltas pas 'grub pa med //
NK103(pe)019:165: rang byung theg pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i lam la gang gnas pa //
NK103(pe)019:166: blos bsam gyis mi khyab par rang lugs su bzhag pa la //
NK103(pe)019:167: chos nyid yid la mi byed pas chos can la
NK103(pe)019:168: yengs pa med pas rnal 'byor rdzogs pa bcos med
NK103(pe)019:169: la // 'dod spyod kyi theg le'i spro bsdu med do //
NK103(pe)019:170: ye nas rdzogs pa rnam dag rang byung ye shes la //
NK103(pe)019:171: bsam gtan gyi yan lag kun dang rang bzhin nam ngang gis ldan pa la //
NK103(pe)019:172: rtog pa ngang bems po'i rlung gis 'jug pa rang bzhin gyis zhi //
NK103(pe)019:173: ye shes 'dod pa'i blos btsal ba med pa'i bde ba la //
NK103(pe)019:174: dga' ba dga' ba mchog dga' dga' bral lhan cig skyes dga' bzhi yi yan lag bcu drug gnas //
NK103(pe)019:175: gsang spyod thabs la ma brten yang //
NK103(pe)019:176: rin chen snang ba'i thabs kyis shes //
NK103(pe)019:177: brda sprod pa'i tshig gi lam la gnas par gyur kyang //
NK103(pe)019:178: thig le rang byung gi dgongs pa gzhan nas ma yin te nyid las 'char //
NK103(pe)019:179: rtog dpyod kyi yan lag gi the tshom dang bral te //
NK103(pe)019:180: sems kyi dga' bde'i rtsol ba med do //
NK103(pe)019:181: rtogs pa'i ngang du gnas pa rtse gcig yengs pa
NK103(pe)019:182: med pa la gnas na ting nge'i ro bde ba'i
NK103(pe)019:183: mtshan nyid ni rang bzhin med pa chos skur gnas
NK103(pe)019:184: // rang byung gi ye shes rang la gnas pas rang snang bar byed pa'i thabs chen dbang gis //
NK103(pe)019:185: 'khrul pa'i sems kyi bag chags thabs kyis ye shes su shes //
NK103(pe)019:186: snang ba rang rig tu de bde ba ru de
NK103(pe)019:187: rig pa 'od gsal du bsgyur ba gsum la de
NK103(pe)019:189: sems kyi bde ba'i ye shes rang la gnas pa'i gter kha dbye //
NK103(pe)019:190: rang byung ye shes 'od gsal ba la //
NK103(pe)019:191: rgyu rkyen med pa'i rig pa nyid ye nas rang gsal //
NK103(pe)019:192: ye shes rang la gnas pas rtsol sgrub med pas bde ba che //
NK103(pe)019:193: 'khor 'das kun mkhyen me long la gzugs brnyan gsal ba lta bu nyid //
NK103(pe)019:194: ma lus pa'i snang ba tha dad rang bzhin gyis dag ste /
NK103(pe)019:195: sems kyi chos nyid bde bar shes //
NK103(pe)019:196: kun bzang nyag gcig la mu mtha' cir ma yang ma mthong //
NK103(pe)019:197: yul du mthong ba med par rang gsal ba'i me long nyid //
NK103(pe)019:198: rang rgyud pa'i dngos po med pa'i rig pa yin //
NK103(pe)019:200: ba rtag pa'i rgyu gang nyid yin brtag grang dang
NK103(pe)019:201: po ltar na bdag gam gzhan nam rgyu de nyid
NK103(pe)019:202: gang yin // bdag las skye na rgyu'i bdag nyid
NK103(pe)019:203: grub pa'am ma grub pa gang gis 'bras bu ji
NK103(pe)019:204: gang yin // ltar bskyed // de ltar ba nyid
NK103(pe)019:205: grub kyang skye dgos na thug pa med par 'gyur
NK103(pe)019:206: gang yin // ltar bskyed // la // de lta
NK103(pe)019:207: min na bdag ma grub pas skyed pa gang zhig
NK103(pe)019:208: gang yin // ltar bskyed // la // ni //
NK103(pe)019:209: nus pa thams cad dang bral ba'i mtshan nyid yin
NK103(pe)019:210: pas rgyu 'bras gnyi ga med par 'gyur ro de
NK103(pe)019:212: gang bdag nyid las gzhan pa'i rgyu las 'bras bu de 'grub na //
NK103(pe)019:213: rgyu gcig las 'bras bu gcig gam du ma zhig
NK103(pe)019:214: skye du ma las 'bras bu gcig gam du ma
NK103(pe)019:216: 'jig rten na rig pa'i skad cig snga mas phyi
NK103(pe)019:217: ma bskyed pa bzhin gcig gis gcig bskyed pa dang
NK103(pe)019:218: / mig gis rigs mthun pa'i skad cig dang rang
NK103(pe)019:219: gi rnam shes bskyed pa ltar gcig gis du ma
NK103(pe)019:220: / dang / 'byung ba bzhi dang sa bon gyis myu gu bskyed pa ltar du mas gcig dang /
NK103(pe)019:221: mtshungs pa de ma thag las rtogs pa'i ngo bo
NK103(pe)019:222: yul las de dang 'dra ba dbang po las yul
NK103(pe)019:224: shes pa'i khyad par du ma bskyed pa ltar rgyu
NK103(pe)019:225: 'bras kyi chos mu bzhi yod pa bzhin du yang
NK103(pe)019:226: dag pa'i ye shes kyang yin na //
NK103(pe)019:227: yang dag pa'i ye shes de slu ba dang chos mthun pas brdzun nam ci //
NK103(pe)019:228: de ltar chos dang gang zag gi bdag tu lta
NK103(pe)019:229: ba log pa bzhin du 'jig rten du 'bras kyang
NK103(pe)019:230: spang bya nyid du 'gyur bas na yang dag min
NK103(pe)019:231: no // 'bras bu dang mi mthun 0par gnas pa
NK103(pe)019:232: dbang phyug dang bdag dang rang bzhin la sogs pa
NK103(pe)019:233: rtag pa'i chos yin par 'dod na //
NK103(pe)019:234: rang rang gi zhen pa'i log rtog nyid du 'gyur ba de nyid tsam du rigs kyi //
NK103(pe)019:235: de lta min te yang dag tu 'dod na rtag
NK103(pe)019:236: pa gang zhig rim dang cig char gyis brtag ngan
NK103(pe)019:238: sngags bskyed pa'i rim pa lha bsgom pa la blo gnas pa thob nas ni //
NK103(pe)019:239: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i don mi rtog pa la gang 'jug par 'dod pa de //
NK103(pe)019:240: lam pa gang gis bskyed rdzogs gang zhig la blo ji ltar gnas te //
NK103(pe)019:241: rtsol ba'i bskyed pa'i lha de la 'jug pa nyid dam //
NK103(pe)019:242: rang gnas kyi ye shes ji lta bar rig pa'i don ting nge 'dzin la 'jug /
NK103(pe)019:243: bskyed rdzogs de nyid de ltar so sor nyams su len pa yin na de lta bu 'thad mod //
NK103(pe)019:244: de lta min na dus gcig gi tshe gang zhig 'thad te //
NK103(pe)019:245: rgyu gcig gis bskyed rdzogs thams cad nas thams cad du grub pa'am //
NK103(pe)019:246: ma yin na bskyed rdzogs gnyis dus gcig la blo gnas pa de la 'thad pa gang //
NK103(pe)019:247: gzhi 'bras dang rjes su mthun rgyu yis 'bras bu'i lam la ma gnas na //
NK103(pe)019:248: rgyu yis 'bras bu bskyed pa de bzhin du rgyu
NK103(pe)019:249: mtshan nyid kyi rjes su mthun pa nyid du 'gyur
NK103(pe)019:250: bas 'bras bu lam du byed par mi 'gyur ro
NK103(pe)019:251: // des na seng ge phrug nyid la rtsal rdzogs pa bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:252: gdod nas sku gsum du lhun gyis grub pas sgrub pa'i rtsol ba med pas bde ba'i lam mo //
NK103(pe)019:253: rtsol bas bsgrubs pas 'bras mthar 'byung ba yin na //
NK103(pe)019:254: 'jig rten gyi rtsol ba'i chos la'ang de bzhin du 'bras bu 'byung ba yin no //
NK103(pe)019:255: de ltar spang bya 'jig rten pa'i chos 'bras bu lha'i dal yin par 'dod pas na //
NK103(pe)019:256: khyod la dag pa'i ye shes nyid gang yin //
NK103(pe)019:257: de ltar 'dod pa nyid na 'bras bu rtag par 'gyur //
NK103(pe)019:258: des na rang byung gi ye shes la yon tan ma lus par rdzogs pa'i lam ni /
NK103(pe)019:259: skyed pa'i rgyu la mi gnas 'bras bu tshol ba'i rtsol ba med de //
NK103(pe)019:260: rang gnas kyi ye shes gdod nas grub pas ye
NK103(pe)019:261: nas grub pa'i rang bzhin de bskyed mi dgos pa
NK103(pe)019:262: ni ye gsal nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //
NK103(pe)019:263: gsal byed kyi rnam pa mi dgos pa ji bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:264: sems nyid la zla ba'i gzugs dang 'dra bar bsgoms pas gsal ba ngang gis 'byung //
NK103(pe)019:265: dbyings kyi 'bras bu blos bsam mi khyab //
NK103(pe)019:266: dngos po dang mtshan ma cir yang mi rtog par 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK103(pe)019:267: che ba'i chos longs sprul sku gsum mu mtha' dpag tu med //
NK103(pe)019:268: ye shes kyi rig pa rang la gnas pa de thug phrad du //
NK103(pe)019:269: gdams ngag rin chen gyi snang bas rtogs pa'i ngang du gzhag par bya //
NK103(pe)019:270: brjod pa dang bral kyang rig pa'i thog babs nyid du //
NK103(pe)019:271: ma btsal bar rang byung bde ba chen po nyid do //
NK103(pe)019:272: yi ge med pa'i gsung mchog yin ste //
NK103(pe)019:273: des kun bzang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ston //
NK103(pe)019:274: chos nyid mi rtog pa'i don dang mjal bas go zhing rig /
NK103(pe)019:275: yi ge med pa dang rang rig 1pa'i 1gsung gis //
NK103(pe)019:276: ljags 2kyi rtse mor ma bskyod kyang //
NK103(pe)019:277: don gyis chos nyid mjal bar ston //
NK103(pe)019:278: gsang sngags kyi yon tan mi zad pa'i gter gyi mdzod mi gtong bar 'dzin cing //
NK103(pe)019:279: rgyal ba'i drag sngags brjod pa'i tha snyad dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:281: phrin las bzhi so sor med pa'i don gyis rang gzhan gyi dgos pa grub //
NK103(pe)019:282: rgyu 'bras dbye ba med kyang 'bras bu mthar thug pa yin no //
NK103(pe)019:283: rig pa mu bzhi'i mtha' dang bral ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK103(pe)019:284: gang du yang zhen med tshul gyis blo 'jug na
NK103(pe)019:285: bde ste de yang dang po rang gi sems kyi
NK103(pe)019:287: gzugs ming sems la rim par bla ma'i gdams ngag bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:288: bsgoms pa'i mngon sum drod dang ldan nas ma bsgoms pa'i mngon sum pas brda don sprad //
NK103(pe)019:289: bkra gsal gzugs la sogs pa dkyil 'khor tshogs drug gi ye shes sgom pa la //
NK103(pe)019:290: brda sprod pa'i sgra yi mtha' la brten nas rtogs pa'i ngang la gzhag par bya //
NK103(pe)019:291: blos myong ba med pa'i rnam pa shar ba yin /
NK103(pe)019:292: tshor ba gsum dang bral ba'i reg byas don go //
NK103(pe)019:293: phyi rol gyi chu bo drag dal gyi tshul bzhin du nyams su nges par brtan par 'gyur te //
NK103(pe)019:294: tha mar dran pa dang rtog pas bsams pa'i rgyu ba'i yid dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:295: dpa' brtul za byed stag gi sems ma btul ba lta bus //
NK103(pe)019:296: shes pa'ang rang sor bzhag ste gnyen pos ma btul la //
NK103(pe)019:297: stag mo lta bu'i sems ma bcos so ma la ni //
NK103(pe)019:298: ye shes kyi rol pa cir yang mi 'gag pas //
NK103(pe)019:299: ched du btsal ba med pa'i ye shes rang rig pa'i ngang yin pa //
NK103(pe)019:300: des na rang bzhin ji ltar yin no cog gi sor 'jog go //
NK103(pe)019:301: phyi nang gi dngos po ji ltar blo la snang ba yang //
NK103(pe)019:302: rang nyid gi shes pa nyid du mthong //
NK103(pe)019:303: dus gsum sangs rgyas lhag ma ma lus pa'i //
NK103(pe)019:304: thugs las bzhag pa'i man ngag gi bcud //
NK103(pe)019:305: gdams pa rin chen la brten nas shar ba'i ngang la rang chas su rdzogs //
NK103(pe)019:306: bya byed kyi rtsol ba dang bral ba'i rig pa mi rtog pa //
NK103(pe)019:307: ma bcos rang byung bde ba'i klong //
NK103(pe)019:308: rang rig pa'i ye shes lhun grub kyi klong du shar //
NK103(pe)019:309: rang byung ye shes kyi nam mkha' lta bur chos kun la khyab //
NK103(pe)019:310: rtogs pa rang gsal rig pa'i ngang la goms pas gnas //
NK103(pe)019:311: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i ye shes thig le che //
NK103(pe)019:312: rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba'i rnam nges las /
NK103(pe)019:313: rnam rtog rjes su 'brel ba la /
NK103(pe)019:314: don gsal snang ba yod ma yin /
NK103(pe)019:317: rang rig yul cir yang mi rtog pa //
NK103(pe)019:318: ye shes rang gsal sems su gsal //
NK103(pe)019:319: sems kyi ngo bo cir yang mi rtog sems su thim //
NK103(pe)019:320: sems kyi ngo bo cir yang ma yin pas phyogs gcig gang du yang dmigs su med //
NK103(pe)019:321: rnam par rtog pa'i sems kyi rgyu ba thams cad dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:322: rig pa ye shes ni gzung ba dang 'dzin pa kun dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:323: ye shes kyi rang snang rang 'od kyi rol pa byang chub sems //
NK103(pe)019:324: rnam pa sgyu ma ye shes bde ba chen po'i klong //
NK103(pe)019:325: mtshan nyid rang rig ye shes la yul snang yang 'dzin pa med de //
NK103(pe)019:326: rang byung sgyu mar mngon sum du gsal //
NK103(pe)019:327: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes ma bcos pa //
NK103(pe)019:328: bde ba'i sgyu mar shar yang rang rig nyid yin pas thams cad ye shes sems su 'char //
NK103(pe)019:329: rig pa'i ye shes la sgrib byed med par 'od gsal bas //
NK103(pe)019:330: chos thams cad ye shes nyid du mtho ste //
NK103(pe)019:331: ye shes ma yin pa'i chos gang yang med //
NK103(pe)019:332: khams gsum gyi dwangs ma'i ye shes nyid ni //
NK103(pe)019:333: ye shes rig cing rtogs pa'i thabs kyis shes //
NK103(pe)019:334: 'gro ba 'khrul pa'i sa nas brda don bkrol te //
NK103(pe)019:335: ye shes rig pas rgyal ba'i gral du gzhag /
NK103(pe)019:336: rtsol bas ma bcos par sku gsung thugs su gnas //
NK103(pe)019:337: rang rig sems kyi rang 'od 'bar ba nyid //
NK103(pe)019:338: ye shes sems kyi phur pa mi 'gyur bar thebs
NK103(pe)019:339: pas rnam par rtog pa bzhon pa'i rta rlung dang
NK103(pe)019:340: bral bas dngos grub bde ba'i rang byung nyid ni
NK103(pe)019:341: thar pa'i lam mchog byang chub sems //
NK103(pe)019:342: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i rig pa nyid //
NK103(pe)019:343: rang byung sems kyi ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid la //
NK103(pe)019:344: chos can gyi rnam pa ji snyed pa rig pa thabs kyis gnas //
NK103(pe)019:345: bcos med rang lugs dgongs pa bde chen 'di //
NK103(pe)019:346: rang rig pa'i mngon sum mthong ba la mu bzhi'i ngos gzung gang yang med //
NK103(pe)019:347: chos nyid rtogs pa rang shar kyang mtshan ma'i dngos por grub pa med //
NK103(pe)019:348: blta ru med pa'i chos nyid bde chen rig pa ma mthong ste //
NK103(pe)019:349: thabs 'di dang bral na rtog pa nyid yin pas //
NK103(pe)019:350: rgyal ba'i bka' yi don dang rtog pa de mi ldan //
NK103(pe)019:351: dmus long mdun na gzugs snang yang mi mthong ba bzhin //
NK103(pe)019:352: 'bras bu mthar phyin rtog pa de la yod ma
NK103(pe)019:353: yin te kun bzang rgyal ba'i yin lugs kyi don
NK103(pe)019:354: dang 'gal // rtog med rang gsal dgongs pa rgyal
NK103(pe)019:355: ba'i thugs rtog pas ma rig /'dzin pa rtog pa'i
NK103(pe)019:356: cha la gang zag gang gnas kyang //
NK103(pe)019:357: 'khor ba'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal nyid du 'gyur //
NK103(pe)019:358: rtog pa'i dbang gis rang 'dod don gyis 'bras bu rtog med mthar ma phyin //
NK103(pe)019:359: ye shes gsal ba bde ba rtog pa med pa'i sa //
NK103(pe)019:360: de mu matha'i phyogs su 'dod pas mi 'grub ste mthar 'dzin gyis thob pa med do //
NK103(pe)019:361: 'o na de gang las 'byung na 'dod med rang bzhag nyid las 'byung //
NK103(pe)019:362: shes pa rang lugs ma bcos so ma nyid ka /
NK103(pe)019:363: kun bzang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yin pa'o //
NK103(pe)019:364: so so skye bo tha mal shes pa 'di nyid
NK103(pe)019:365: la nor ba gzhan du bsal ba'i sems med de
NK103(pe)019:367: rang sar bzhag pa ka rgyal ba'i dgongs pa yin no //
NK103(pe)019:368: bla ma nges pa chu bo bzhi yi don la
NK103(pe)019:369: gnas pas yid ches te bla ma nyid la gus
NK103(pe)019:370: // rin chen gadmas ngaga sems kyi gter du 'chang //
NK103(pe)019:371: rgyud lung tshig gi lam gis don lam dgongs pa'i don nges par gsal te //
NK103(pe)019:372: dbang rig pa la rang shar bas gtan la phebs //
NK103(pe)019:373: 'bras bu phebs pa'i ngang du goms pas mi 'gyur rdo rje sems la 'chang //
NK103(pe)019:374: ma nor nges pa'i ston pa rang rig pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen nyid yin pas //
NK103(pe)019:375: don la brgyud nas 'dren pa drang ba'i don la sems mi 'jug /
NK103(pe)019:376: phyi rol kheng grags kyi 'dod rtsol sems dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:377: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi bka' nas gsungs pa la yid mi 'gyur //
NK103(pe)019:378: bla ma rin chen rang gi srog tu 'dzin cing //
NK103(pe)019:379: mos pas rang gi 'dod pa rgyal srid rang lus 'khor g.yog la sogs gang gces gtong //
NK103(pe)019:380: rin chen gter gyi man ngag 'di //
NK103(pe)019:381: srog dang bral ba shi ba'i kha bzhin du snod min la bsdam mo //
NK103(pe)019:382: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems nyid 'di la //
NK103(pe)019:383: ye shes dang ma rig gnyis tha dad med de //
NK103(pe)019:384: 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang ma 'khrul pa gnyi ga
NK103(pe)019:385: rig par byang chub kyi sems rang byung gi ye
NK103(pe)019:386: shes su gcig ste rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK103(pe)019:387: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK103(pe)019:388: phyin ci log nyid yang dag ste //
NK103(pe)019:389: nyon mongs sdug bsngal byang chub mchog /
NK103(pe)019:391: rigs drug gi zhen rtog gi brtags pa mi mthun pa sna tshogs dang //
NK103(pe)019:392: rang byung gi ye shes 'od gsal gyi ngo bo nyid //
NK103(pe)019:393: gcig gang du gcig na 'od gsal rang byung sems
NK103(pe)019:394: su gcig ste de'i ngo bo gang yin na byang
NK103(pe)019:395: chub sems la ngo bo 'di 'dra'o zhes pa dang
NK103(pe)019:396: bral lo de lta bu'i don dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK103(pe)019:397: 'byor pas 'khor ba ye shes nyid du mthong //
NK103(pe)019:398: rang rang bsam pas phyin ci log tu brtags pa'i
NK103(pe)019:399: zhen pa sna tshogs pa ni thog ma med pa
NK103(pe)019:400: can gyi 'du byed sna tshogs kyi bag chags yin
NK103(pe)019:401: don las log pa'i rkyen gyis mthong ngo //
NK103(pe)019:402: rang rig pa'i ye shes yin don la 'jug pa dang //
NK103(pe)019:403: phyi ci log tu brtags pa'i bag chags dngos po gnyis ni //
NK103(pe)019:404: grib ma lus bzhin grub pa dang bde ba gcig /
NK103(pe)019:405: byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid ni rgyu la mi
NK103(pe)019:406: gnas te rang snang yin pas thog ma dang bral
NK103(pe)019:407: tha ma med // dus thog ma med pa 'khor ba'i rang bzhin 'khrul pa 'di //
NK103(pe)019:408: byang chub sems rang byung ye shes la ye nas
NK103(pe)019:409: dag ste gsang ba las 'khor ba rnam par dag
NK103(pe)019:411: sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu bsgribs pa med pa yin pa la //
NK103(pe)019:412: glo bur du gzugs snang sprin gyis bsgribs kyang sprin
NK103(pe)019:413: nam mkha'i ngo bo ma yin te rkyen gyis snang
NK103(pe)019:415: me'i rkyen dang ldan pa'i lcags kyi gnas skabs kyi
NK103(pe)019:416: rang bzhin tsha ba dang 'dra bar 'khrul pa gshis
NK103(pe)019:418: glo bur gyi rkyen gyis snang ngo //
NK103(pe)019:420: rang bzhin gnas lugs dang bral ba ma yin te //
NK103(pe)019:421: gshis la skye 'gag med pas dus gsum ma yin te nam mkha' bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:422: chos sku rang bzhin ye nas rnam par dag /
NK103(pe)019:423: longs spyod rang rig dngos po thams cad la bde longs spyod pas bde ba nyid //
NK103(pe)019:424: sprul pa 'gro 'ong med par khyab pas chu zla lta bur snang //
NK103(pe)019:425: de gsum dbyer med rig pa gcig gi ngang ngo //
NK103(pe)019:426: bzang po blang ngan pa dor gnyis bral mnyam pa nyid //
NK103(pe)019:427: byang chub sems kyi ye shes la //
NK103(pe)019:428: snying po mnyam nyid ye sangs rgyas //
NK103(pe)019:429: snying po don la sa lam gyi rtsol ba med //
NK103(pe)019:430: don gyi rang byung la 'khrul grol gnyis su med //
NK103(pe)019:431: sems kyi rang rig pa rtog pa nyid du shar
NK103(pe)019:432: ba'i rnam rtog rang byung ye shes rtog med nyid
NK103(pe)019:433: du rang 'bar ba ni rtsol bas btsal ba med
NK103(pe)019:434: pa'i 'bras bu mthar thug pa nyid do //
NK103(pe)019:435: rgyal ba'i bka' yi bcud bsdus pa'i snying po man ngag rin po che 'di //
NK103(pe)019:436: rgya mtsho'i bcud bsdus pa bzhin du bdud rtsir 'dus //
NK103(pe)019:437: snying po'i don ston pa'i man ngag 'di gsang ba'i man ngag rnams kyi bcud do //
NK103(pe)019:438: gsal ba'i sgron ma'i 'od kyi snying po 'di //
NK103(pe)019:439: bka'i bcud ma lus 'dus pa'i gsung gi 'khor lo yin //
NK103(pe)019:440: snying po brjod pa'i gsung gis rtogs par bya ba ni //
NK103(pe)019:441: sems nyid rang byung snying po nyid do //
NK103(pe)019:442: de nyid du phyi 1rdul tshon nang 1rtsa gsang ba mkha'i dkyil 111'khor 'dus //
NK103(pe)019:443: 'og ma ltar dal du 'byung ba dang 'jug pa mi mnga' snying por gsal //
NK103(pe)019:444: rang byung ye shes rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dgongs par gnas //
NK103(pe)019:445: ye shes snying po nam mkha' dang 'dra ba ste mtha' dbus mi mnga' blang dor med //
NK103(pe)019:446: gzhan nas mi len snying po bdag med gsal //
NK103(pe)019:447: bka' yi bcud bsdus snying po 'di //
NK103(pe)019:448: gnas lugs rang bzhin snying po byang chub sems kyi
NK103(pe)019:449: sman chen rtsol med rtogs pas 'khor ba sdug bsngal
NK103(pe)019:451: byang chub sems kyi sman med na //
NK103(pe)019:452: lus ngag gi rtsol bas dge ba'i don la 'jug pa mtho ris kyi rgyu //
NK103(pe)019:453: byang chub sems kyi sman chen rang la gnas bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:454: de la mi rtog par byang chub sems kyi sman chen gzhan nas 'tshol bar byed //
NK103(pe)019:455: rnyed du med pa'i tshul gyis rnyed de rtogs pas
NK103(pe)019:456: gzhan nas ma 'ongs te rang sems nyid sman chen
NK103(pe)019:457: du mthong ngo // rtogs pas gzhan nas ma 'ongs te //
NK103(pe)019:458: rang byung snying po ni thog ma med pa nas
NK103(pe)019:459: rang la gnas te spros bral nam mkha' lta bu
NK103(pe)019:460: nyid // rgyal ba'i ye shes kyi sku dang rang bzhin ldan te //
NK103(pe)019:461: phyi gzung ba dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems dang bral ba'i ngang la rtag par bzhugs //
NK103(pe)019:462: bde ba'i don la ma chags rol //
NK103(pe)019:463: snang ba thams cad rang byung ye shes rang rig par gnas //
NK103(pe)019:464: byang chub sems kyi sman chen 'di //
NK103(pe)019:465: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ste //
NK103(pe)019:466: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyi lam du bde //
NK103(pe)019:467: bsam gyis mi khyab dgongs pa'i don ni //
NK103(pe)019:468: shes pa ma bcos par rang bzhag so ma nyid do //
NK103(pe)019:469: snying po de lta bu'i don rtogs nas gtang gzhag gi bya ba bral //
NK103(pe)019:470: rtag par rang gsal rig pa'i ngang la bzhugs //
NK103(pe)019:471: skyon bcos su med ting nge 'dzin du 'dzin pa dang bral phar 'phro tshur 'du med //
NK103(pe)019:472: byang chub snying po la rnam par rtog pa'i rgyu ba bral //
NK103(pe)019:473: chos kun 'byung yang rang rig pa rang byung ye shes la 'pho 'gyur med //
NK103(pe)019:474: rgyal ba'i thugs rje yang rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK103(pe)019:475: la rtsol ba dang bral ba rang snang gi byin rlabs las 'byung ste //
NK103(pe)019:476: phyogs ris mi mnga' kun la khyab //
NK103(pe)019:477: gnas lugs snying po nyid du 'gro ba kun sgrol bar mdzad pa ni snying rje'o //
NK103(pe)019:478: byamsa pas 'gro ba thams cad chos nyid ngang du bskyabs //
NK103(pe)019:479: dga' ba rang rig rang byung ye shes dang mi 'bral ba //
NK103(pe)019:480: blang dor gnyis med btang snyoms che //
NK103(pe)019:481: rang byung snying po 'khor lo'i don la //
NK103(pe)019:482: rtog pa dang bral 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rnam par
NK103(pe)019:483: dag /'byed pa med pa'i thugs rje la sems can
NK103(pe)019:484: du grub pa med pas don mi mdzad de yang
NK103(pe)019:486: de phyir phan mdzad brtser ldan byang chub brnyes nas ni /
NK103(pe)019:487: sems tshogs sus shes snyam nas thugs khral chung bar mdzad /
NK103(pe)019:489: yul gyi dngos po dang sems dmigs pa mi mnga' rang byung sems //
NK103(pe)019:490: 'od gsal snying po rdzogs pa 'di'i don bla ma rin chen gsung gi brtag pas shes te //
NK103(pe)019:491: 'gro drug sems can thams cad la //
NK103(pe)019:492: rang gnas kyi ye shes nyid ldan pa de //
NK103(pe)019:493: brtag pa gsum gyis shes par 'gyur ba ni chos sku //
NK103(pe)019:494: ming la brtag pa dang longs sku sems la brtags te ye shes tshol //
NK103(pe)019:495: sprul sku yul lnga'i dngos po gang yang rung ba dang gsum la //
NK103(pe)019:496: brtags pas rang log pa dang rang sar log pa'i
NK103(pe)019:497: shes pa 'byung ba ni nor bu rin chen gser
NK103(pe)019:499: lce mnan na na ta'i yig ge'i sgra la sogs pa brjod tu mi btub pa ltar //
NK103(pe)019:500: de bzhin du rten 'brel lus la brtag pa la sogs pa'i gnas skabs gzhan du yang //
NK103(pe)019:501: snying po ye shes ngos gzung bar bya //
NK103(pe)019:502: bka'i snying po'i gsung 'di rnal ma'i don dang 'brel //
NK103(pe)019:503: rnal 'byor pa skal ldan rin chen lta bu yis //
NK103(pe)019:504: 'byung ba'i dus drug ni grub mtha' ngan pa la gnas pa'i dus su //
NK103(pe)019:505: man ngag 'di yis don kun rig par gyis shig /
NK103(pe)019:506: gal te 'di yis rang sems ma rig na //
NK103(pe)019:507: rtog ge sgra'am tshad ma gang gis kyang //
NK103(pe)019:508: rig pa'i rang byung ye shes rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK103(pe)019:509: gzhi nyid rang byung dus gsum du 'gyur ba med //
NK103(pe)019:510: de rtogs pa'i rang byung sems kyi lam //
NK103(pe)019:511: de'i ngang du goms pas ma yengs par byang chub sems su gsal //
NK103(pe)019:512: rang byung gi 'bras bu mthar phyin pa rnams //
NK103(pe)019:513: 'gro don mdzad pa ni yin don rtogs pas sgrib
NK103(pe)019:514: pa las grol te gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum 'od
NK103(pe)019:515: gsal dbyer med gcig gi ngang yin pas so //
NK103(pe)019:516: byang chub sems kyi rang rig rang byung ye shes
NK103(pe)019:517: 'di la bag chags 'khrul pa'i dri mas bsgos pa'i
NK103(pe)019:518: dbang gis na // zhen pas brtags pa'i 'du byed
NK103(pe)019:519: sna tshogs thag pa la sbrul ltar med bzhin grub
NK103(pe)019:520: de ltar 'khrul pa'i sems kyi bag chags bzang ngan
NK103(pe)019:521: dbang gis na // cir snang yang // rig pa
NK103(pe)019:522: 'od gsal la gzhi lam 'bras bu'i dus gsum kar
NK103(pe)019:523: dbang gis na // cir snang yang // 'gyur ba
NK103(pe)019:524: med // sna tshogs su snang ba'i rang bzhin 'di
NK103(pe)019:525: dbang gis na // cir snang yang // 'gyur ba
NK103(pe)019:526: med // // bka'i snying po gsung gi brjod bya
NK103(pe)019:527: dbang gis na // cir snang yang // 'gyur ba
NK103(pe)019:528: med // // yin ste // 'khrul pa ma yin
NK103(pe)019:529: te 'khrul pa de las rang log rang sar log
NK103(pe)019:530: dbang gis na // cir snang yang // 'gyur ba
NK103(pe)019:531: med // // yin ste // par snang bas //
NK103(pe)019:532: sna tshogs kyi snang ba 'di rang rig byang chub
NK103(pe)019:534: 'khrul pa'i rtog pa'i rtsa ba ni byang chub sems //
NK103(pe)019:535: rang rig sems la rtog par 'khrul ba yang //
NK103(pe)019:536: ya mtshams thog ma med pa'i dus nas dmigs pa
NK103(pe)019:537: sna tshogs kyi bag chags kyi dbang du gyur pa
NK103(pe)019:538: dang // rin chen gdams ngag rkyen med pas //
NK103(pe)019:539: rtog med snying po rnal ma'i sems ma goms pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:540: thag pa sbrul min yang sbrul du snang ba bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:541: 'du byed kyi dngos po sna tshogs snang ba'i rang
NK103(pe)019:542: bzhin 'di'i rang bzhin chos nyid yin pas gnas lugs
NK103(pe)019:544: rgyal ba sku gsum gyi dgongs pa gsal ba'i sems nyid la //
NK103(pe)019:545: chos nyid ma yin bag tsam yang mi snang thams cad snang ba'i ngo bo sems nyid 'di /
NK103(pe)019:546: rang byung ye shes snying po nyid du mthong ngo rtogs so //
NK103(pe)019:547: ngo bo nyid la tshig brjod pa bral //
NK103(pe)019:548: rang bzhin rnam dag rig pa byang chub sems la //
NK103(pe)019:549: brjod du med kyang tshig don du ma brjod na tha snyad la ni ma brten par //
NK103(pe)019:550: dam pa'i don ni rtogs mi 'gyur //
NK103(pe)019:552: rig pa'i don dang mjal ba med des na brjod pa'i sgra la sems brgyud de drangs pas //
NK103(pe)019:553: ma bcos rang byung chos nyid du mthong ngo //
NK103(pe)019:554: rang rig sems la don rtogs na //
NK103(pe)019:555: blo 'jug pa'i thabs bya byed mi gnyis tshul gyis gnas //
NK103(pe)019:556: bgrod med cig car du lam gyi cha rkyen rdzogs
NK103(pe)019:557: pa'i bde ba che na po ni grub matha'i phyogs
NK103(pe)019:558: su ma lhungs gzu bo drang po'i sems //
NK103(pe)019:559: rdzogs pa'i ye shes snying po la //
NK103(pe)019:560: rtsol ba'i rim pa'i lam med mthar phyin sa //
NK103(pe)019:561: rang byung rtogs pa'i ngang du 'jug pa la //
NK103(pe)019:562: de kho na nyid snying po rnal ma'i don rtogs pas //
NK103(pe)019:563: 'bras bu sku gnyis 'dod pa'i tshogs gnyis la yid
NK103(pe)019:564: mi 'jug kyang rdzogs pa de bzhin du pha rol
NK103(pe)019:566: rang byung rdzogs pa'i sems la gnas //
NK103(pe)019:567: rtog dpyod kyi bsam pa dang bral cir yang mi rtog pa'i dgongs pa la /
NK103(pe)019:568: de nyid du pha rol phyin drug ni /
NK103(pe)019:570: dbul ba 'dor bar byed pa dang //
NK103(pe)019:571: bsil ba thob dang khro bzod dang //
NK103(pe)019:572: mchog sbyor ba dang yid 'dzin dang //
NK103(pe)019:573: don dam shes pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK103(pe)019:576: mi rtog bzod 'dzin sbyin med tshul khrims la gnas //
NK103(pe)019:577: ma yengs bsam rig pa rgyun brtson mi 'chad //
NK103(pe)019:578: dmigs med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK103(pe)019:580: snga rabs pa rnams stong pa nyid bco brgyad dang sbyar nas gsung ste /
NK103(pe)019:581: gzhung gi dgongs par mi gsal bas ma bris so //
NK103(pe)019:582: sems nyid stong pa mtshan nyid dngos po med pa la //
NK103(pe)019:583: chos nyid dang chon can gang yang tha dad du mi gnas te //
NK103(pe)019:584: dbyer med bde ba chen po snying po rnal ma'i
NK103(pe)019:585: don yin la de ltar dngos po med kyang ye
NK103(pe)019:586: shes kyi rol pa sna tshogs 'gag ma yin //
NK103(pe)019:587: bden brdzun gnyis mthar mi 'dzin pa yis //
NK103(pe)019:588: snying po'i don la rtogs par 'dod pa'i blo dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:589: kun bzang rang byung ye shes 'od gsal ba ni
NK103(pe)019:590: rtog dpyod kyi bsam pa thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK103(pe)019:591: ye shes nam mkha' cir yang mi rtog pa dang
NK103(pe)019:592: 'dra ste // de nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ma bcos pa rnal ma'o //
NK103(pe)019:593: dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba chos nyid dbyings kyi thugs //
NK103(pe)019:594: cir yang mi 'gag pa'i ye shes ni rang rig pa'i gsung //
NK103(pe)019:595: snang stong ngam 'khor 'das dbyer med chos kyi sku gzung 'dzin dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:596: rang rgyud pa'i sku gsung thugs dang bral ba'i rang byung gi sku gsung thugs //
NK103(pe)019:597: phyi yul dang nang shes pa mi mnga' bar rang gsal ba nyid la yid //
NK103(pe)019:598: phyir 'byung ba dang nang du 'jug pa mi mnga' bar rang bzhin gyis gnas //
NK103(pe)019:599: dbang po lnga'i ngo la snang ba'i yul lnga rnams //
NK103(pe)019:600: snang la mi 'dzin pas chos nyid byang chub sems su mthong //
NK103(pe)019:601: nyon mongs lnga po ye shes lnga'i lam //
NK103(pe)019:602: chos thams cad byang chub sems kyi gzhi ste //
NK103(pe)019:603: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin pas so //
NK103(pe)019:604: sangs rgyas su dag pa'i sems la btsal med de //
NK103(pe)019:605: ched du btsal ba'i kun rdzob ni nor bas des 'bras bu grub ma yin //
NK103(pe)019:606: dam pa'i don rnal ma la gang 'jug pa //
NK103(pe)019:607: sems nyid gsang ba yon tan thams cad rdzogs pa'i don nyid la //
NK103(pe)019:608: chos nyid gsang ba'i don la dmigs te bla ma'i //
NK103(pe)019:609: nges pa'i gdams ngag zab mo yis //
NK103(pe)019:610: btsal med rang sor bzhag pa'i btsal ba dang //
NK103(pe)019:611: mi sgom rang lugs su gnas pa'i sgom pa dang //
NK103(pe)019:612: phyogs su mi gnas pa'i tshul la gnas pa dang //
NK103(pe)019:613: dmigs pa la bzhag 'jog med pa'i mnyam bzhag rang
NK103(pe)019:614: byung ba chen po mi rtog pa'i don la ched
NK103(pe)019:615: du ma btsal ba'i gyi na ba //
NK103(pe)019:616: dge dang mi dge'i rnam rtog bral ba ni //
NK103(pe)019:617: byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK103(pe)019:618: rang byung ye shes btsal bas rtogs pa min //
NK103(pe)019:619: byang chub 'dod pa'i blo la byang chub med //
NK103(pe)019:620: yang dag don gyi snying po 'di //
NK103(pe)019:621: rtsol bas btsal bas rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK103(pe)019:622: rtsol ba la zhen pa'i sems nyid las 'byung bar
NK103(pe)019:623: mi 'gyur bas rtsol med du nyal ba'i bsam gtan
NK103(pe)019:624: 'khor lo bade'o // chos can ma lus byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK103(pe)019:625: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems mnyam par bzhag pa la //
NK103(pe)019:626: dngos po med de byang chub rang byung ye shes kyi ngang ni //
NK103(pe)019:627: 'dus ma byas pas bde ba chen po'i klong ngo //
NK103(pe)019:628: sems nyid blos bsam du med ngag tu brjod pa
NK103(pe)019:629: las 'das te dus ye nas rang rnam par dag
NK103(pe)019:630: cing bsam du med brjod du med do //
NK103(pe)019:631: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ba'i rig pa yis //
NK103(pe)019:632: de la ma btsal bar gnas na bsgom zhes bya //
NK103(pe)019:633: rig pa'i chos kyi dbyings la yan par bzhag na //
NK103(pe)019:634: btsal ba'i nad bral bsgom pa yin //
NK103(pe)019:635: de bas snying po sems nyid la 'khrul pa'i dri ma med //
NK103(pe)019:636: pas rig pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyid du bsgom //
NK103(pe)019:637: de ltar 'od gsal sems la gnas 'gyur na //
NK103(pe)019:638: rnam rtog mtshan ma rang bzhin nam ngang gis zhi
NK103(pe)019:639: ste de ltar skye ba med pa'i skye med las
NK103(pe)019:641: rang snang kun bzang gi rol pa 'grub //
NK103(pe)019:642: dngos med dang dngos po la blo mi dmigs shing //
NK103(pe)019:643: dbu ma tsam du 'dzin pa'i sems dang bral te yid kyi rgyu ba bral lo //
NK103(pe)019:644: de ltar sems kyi rgyu ba med pas na //
NK103(pe)019:645: chos thams cad rang byung ye shes stong pa nyid do //
NK103(pe)019:646: sems nyid rig pa rang byung la //
NK103(pe)019:647: cir yang 'gyur ba med de spros bral du gsal bas na //
NK103(pe)019:648: brjod pa'i yi ge med pa'i snying po gsung //
NK103(pe)019:649: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems la gnas //
NK103(pe)019:650: rgyal ba'i dam tshig ma bcos pa ni ched du bsrung ba med pa'i tshul gyis bsrung //
NK103(pe)019:651: thig le nyag gcig las 'gyur ba med pa'i phyag rgya la //
NK103(pe)019:652: cir yang bsgyur ba med pa'i don gyi rgyas btab //
NK103(pe)019:653: 'khor mtha' dang gtso bo dbus med pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK103(pe)019:654: ye shes kyi phar 'phro tshur 'du ba'i ting nge med par gsal //
NK103(pe)019:655: bsam bral la rtag tu rang bzhag ni de nyid rgyal ba'i thugs //
NK103(pe)019:656: te des na chos thams cad byang chub sems las 'da' ba med //
NK103(pe)019:657: sa 'dzin byi ba'am seng ge'i rnam pa'i sems bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:658: 'bras bu gzhan nas rnyed par mi 'gyur te //
NK103(pe)019:659: brtags na rang sems nyid la thug pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:660: byi ba'i bu mo sbyin sa btsal ba'i phyir nyi ma /
NK103(pe)019:663: ri la dris pas mthar rang la thug pa'am /
NK103(pe)019:664: seng ge'i gong na gzhan med pas 'jigs shing nyam
NK103(pe)019:665: nga ba med pa dang 'dra'o gsung pas gzhi la
NK103(pe)019:666: rang sor bzhag pa las gzhan thob par 'dod pa
NK103(pe)019:667: dang bral // rang sems rig pa dus gsum du 'gyur ba med //
NK103(pe)019:668: gzhi ji bzhin pa cir yang mi rtog pa ni chos kyi sku //
NK103(pe)019:669: rtsol ba'i bya ba dang bral yon tan lhun grub gzhi ji bzhin du gnas //
NK103(pe)019:670: rang byung 'od gsal la 'khrul pa ye nas dag /
NK103(pe)019:671: mu mtha' cir yang mi dgongs pas blos bsam mi khyab //
NK103(pe)019:672: rtogs pa'i shes rab dang 'byed pa med pa'i snying
NK103(pe)019:673: rje dang ldan pas 'bras bus rtsol med du 'grub
NK103(pe)019:674: bo // snying po byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK103(pe)019:675: cir yang bsam du med par rang lugs su bzhag
NK103(pe)019:676: pa ni rgyal ba'i thugs su lhun gyis grub pa
NK103(pe)019:678: steng sgo 'khor lo'am 'og sgo rig ma la brten pa'i bde ba yis //
NK103(pe)019:679: rang gnas lhan cig skyes pa'i rig pa ye shes tshol ba nyid ni //
NK103(pe)019:680: rnam rtog yin te don la des rnyed pa min //
NK103(pe)019:681: chags pa'i 'du shes can drang ba'i don du gsungs pa yin gyi //
NK103(pe)019:682: nges par na spros bral rang byung gi sems de //
NK103(pe)019:683: chags pa'i lam gyis shes par mi 'gyur ro //
NK103(pe)019:684: gtsang blang rme dor ba med pa'i brtul zhugs kyang //
NK103(pe)019:685: nges par brtags na don la blang dor nyid du 'gyur //
NK103(pe)019:686: rang rig bsam bral du ched du blos bzhag pa de //
NK103(pe)019:687: don la dngos po 'dzin pa'i zhen par gnas so //
NK103(pe)019:688: 'dir rang byung gi ye shes 'od gsal byang chub snying po 'di ni dngos por zhen pa'i //
NK103(pe)019:689: mtshan ma med pa'i rang bzhin pas //
NK103(pe)019:690: shes rab dang thabs gnyis kyi phan tshun bde ba'i chags pa dang bral //
NK103(pe)019:691: thig le la brten nas 'bras bu 'dod pa'i rtsol
NK103(pe)019:692: ba phar spro ba dang tshur bsdu ba med do
NK103(pe)019:693: // rang rig thabs lam gyi rtsol ba dang bral ba bde ba chen po'i sems de //
NK103(pe)019:694: shes rab dang thabs la so sor mi 'dzin par snyoms par 'jug pas //
NK103(pe)019:695: rtsol med kyi bde ba'i bsam gtan chen po yin //
NK103(pe)019:696: sgyu ma'i ro bde stong la ma chags pas //
NK103(pe)019:697: chags pa med pa'i ye shes la lam gyi cha rkyen thams cad rdzogs pa'i lam //
NK103(pe)019:698: byang chub sems kyi rig pa rang gsal 'di //
NK103(pe)019:699: dngos por 'dzin pa med pa'i shes rab dang thabs kyis 'grub nam mkha' che las kyang //
NK103(pe)019:700: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK103(pe)019:701: shes rab thabs la brten pas 'grub //
NK103(pe)019:702: ming tsam gzhan la brten 'dra yang //
NK103(pe)019:703: mngon sum bde ba rang las 'byung //
NK103(pe)019:705: snang ba gsal ba'i 'khor lo rig pa 'di //
NK103(pe)019:706: mu matha'i ngo bo ma grub la snang du btub
NK103(pe)019:707: pa ni me shel la me dngos su med kyang
NK103(pe)019:708: rkyen dang phrad na 'byung ba dang 'dra //
NK103(pe)019:709: dngos med kyi ye shes de mthong bas 'khrul pa rang sar grol //
NK103(pe)019:710: gzugs sgra sogs yul lngar snang ba rnams blos phyin ci log tu brtags pa yin te //
NK103(pe)019:711: dngos po'i rang bzhin thams cad ni //
NK103(pe)019:712: chos nyid dbyings kyi thig le yin 0no //
NK103(pe)019:713: de 0nyid bsgrub pa'i thabs su ni //
NK103(pe)019:714: snying po'i don rig pa'i nyi ma shar bas //
NK103(pe)019:715: mu mtha' yi mun pa ngang gis ma spangs par dag /
NK103(pe)019:716: rtsol bas bsgrub med rang byung gi bsgrub pa 'dis //
NK103(pe)019:717: khams gsum thams cad 'od gsal gyi thugs byang chub sems su grub //
NK103(pe)019:718: chos thams cad rang sems rig pa'i spyod par bde //
NK103(pe)019:719: rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi spyod pas rang lugs su bzhag pa nyid du //
NK103(pe)019:720: gsal nas so so'i 'dod pa'i grub pa'i mtha' mi 'gegs te //
NK103(pe)019:721: 'gro 'dul thugs rje tshogs kyi bsod nams dkar spyod dge ba rnams ni //
NK103(pe)019:722: rang byung rig pa rtogs par gyur nas kyang //
NK103(pe)019:723: mos pa'i 'gro ba gzhan brgyud nas don la drang phyir rgyun mi bcad //
NK103(pe)019:724: snying po sems kyi don rig na //
NK103(pe)019:725: rang gnas kyi ye shes mthar phyin te 'bras bu chos skur gnas //
NK103(pe)019:726: gzhan longs sku mtshan dang dpe byad bzang po dang ldan pa rang bzhin 'grub //
NK103(pe)019:727: sprul pa'i sku 'gro ba rang rang gi 'dod pa bzhin cir yang 'byung //
NK103(pe)019:728: chu gsal ba'i nang du ri bong can gyi gzugs brnyan 'char ba bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:729: ye shes lus can gyi de bzhin gshegs pas //
NK103(pe)019:730: me shel gyi gzugs ltar du snang nas 'gro ba sgrol //
NK103(pe)019:731: ye shes rang byung de bzhin gshegs pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:732: yan lag mi mnga' rtsis las 'das pa yang lam
NK103(pe)019:733: mthar phyin btang snyoms chen po'i dga' ba rig par
NK103(pe)019:734: rang gsal // dgongs pa rang bzhag gi ngang du ye sangs rgyas pas /
NK103(pe)019:735: rig pa rang shar chos rnams la blos gang du'ang bsam du med par gnas //
NK103(pe)019:736: de ltar byang chub sems nyid la //
NK103(pe)019:737: ma rig pa gdod nas med pas des na 'khor ba'ang med /
NK103(pe)019:738: des na sems can skye ba rgyu ma rig pa gdod nas mi gnas //
NK103(pe)019:739: rang byung ye shes kyi sems rtog pa med pa la rtag par bzhugs te //
NK103(pe)019:740: srid pa 'khor ba'i chos la rgyu med pas na //
NK103(pe)019:741: mya ngan 'das pa'i lam dang bral lo //
NK103(pe)019:742: gzod ma nas ma skyes pa yi chos rnams la //
NK103(pe)019:743: dus nam du yang skye bar mi 'gyur te //
NK103(pe)019:744: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis rang bzhin de nyid du gcig /
NK103(pe)019:745: sems rang byung kyi ye shes gsang ba 'di //
NK103(pe)019:746: snying po don yin la de khyad par rmad du byung ba'i //
NK103(pe)019:747: rang byung chen po'i chos thams kyi bdag po ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK103(pe)019:748: 'khrul pa rang sar dag pa'i don ldan chos kyi sku //
NK103(pe)019:749: rang rig bde ba chen po'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK103(pe)019:750: gnyis su med pa'i thugs rje yis sna tshogs su snang ba sprul pa'i sku rnams //
NK103(pe)019:751: ngo bo tha dad du ma grub ste gsang ba'i byang chub sems //
NK103(pe)019:752: rang byung gi ye shes la gzugs sku snang ba
NK103(pe)019:753: dang chos sku mi snang ba dbyer med pa nyid
NK103(pe)019:754: do // yod pa dang med pa kun gyi ngo bo byang chub kyi sems //
NK103(pe)019:755: rang snang bas rang rig pa las tha dad pa //
NK103(pe)019:756: lha dang gzhal yas khang la sogs pa'i don dang rtags la sogs pa rnams //
NK103(pe)019:757: rnam pa tha dad du 'dzin pa'i bag chags kyi
NK103(pe)019:758: stobs kyi snang ba yin pas yang dag ma yin
NK103(pe)019:760: bsam zhing sgom pa'i dbang gis tha dad de ltar du snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK103(pe)019:761: bde gshegs ye shes gsang ba'i don de /
NK103(pe)019:762: ma mthong ste rnam rtog spros pa la 'chel bas //
NK103(pe)019:763: de la stong nyid rig pa'i man ngag sbyin //
NK103(pe)019:764: dran rtog rig pa'i rlung gis rgyu ba dbral //
NK103(pe)019:765: de'i mtha' ru ma skyes pa'i bsam gtan bya //
NK103(pe)019:766: chos can dang chos nyid gang yang min te //
NK103(pe)019:767: nam mkha' lta bu bdag dang sems can med pa'i //
NK103(pe)019:768: ye shes te bdag gis stong pa'i ngo bo 'o //
NK103(pe)019:769: rang bzhin stong pa la dngos pa'i mtshan med pa //
NK103(pe)019:770: stong mtshan smon pa'i rnam thar gsum ldan bde ba che //
NK103(pe)019:771: de la chags med gzhi yin lugs dang mthun pa
NK103(pe)019:772: yi lam nas 'jug pa ni mtshan ma med pa
NK103(pe)019:773: yang dag pa'i lam la gnas pas na //
NK103(pe)019:774: rang byung ye shes rtogs pa'i 'bras bu ngang gis thig le'i klong du 'char //
NK103(pe)019:775: shar ba'i yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK103(pe)019:776: rang rig ye shes snang ba la //
NK103(pe)019:777: dngos po kun tu rang 'od 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor rnam rang bzhiin gyis gsal bar mi zad pa //
NK103(pe)019:778: rgyan gyi 'khor lo ni sku yi ngang //
NK103(pe)019:779: gang la yang chags bral grags pa ni gsung gi rig pa'i rgyan //
NK103(pe)019:780: dran rig thams cad thugs ye shes su gsal ba'i ting 'dzin nyid //
NK103(pe)019:781: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo blos bsam du med //
NK103(pe)019:782: sgro 'dogs dang skur 'debs dang bral ba stong pa nyid zhi gnas la //
NK103(pe)019:783: 'du shes gang du yang 'jug pa med de blo mnyam par bzhag na //
NK103(pe)019:784: mtshan ma med pas zhi gnas dang lhag mthong zung du 'brel lo //
NK103(pe)019:785: 'di lta bu la mos pas 'jug ci lam la
NK103(pe)019:786: rnal 'byor pa gang gnas pa ni rnam par mi
NK103(pe)019:787: rtog pa gsal ba'i don gyis go //
NK103(pe)019:788: bsam dang bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK103(pe)019:789: snying po'i gnas lugs don la rtogs pas 'jug go //
NK103(pe)019:790: de lta bu'i thabs dang bral ba'i lam gyi rig pas rtsol bas 'bras bu tshol ba ni /
NK103(pe)019:791: ra gan las gser 'byung bar 'dod pa de bzhin no //
NK103(pe)019:792: de ltar 'dod pa'i sems dang ma bral na //
NK103(pe)019:793: snying po'i phyogs med kyi don la bdag tu 'dzin par byed //
NK103(pe)019:794: bde ba'i sems la re ba na //
NK103(pe)019:795: rang rang gi lta ba rtogs pa'i rjes su ting
NK103(pe)019:796: nges 'jug cing zhi gnas kyi 'bras bu tshol lo
NK103(pe)019:797: // rang gi lus nyid sems su ma rtogs par //
NK103(pe)019:798: lus 'dra 'bag lha yi rnam pa bzung nas tha mal gyi //
NK103(pe)019:799: lus kyi dben pas chos nyid tshol ba ni 'khrul lo //
NK103(pe)019:800: rang lus sems su shes pa na //
NK103(pe)019:801: gnas gang na lus gnas kyang sems nyid dben //
NK103(pe)019:802: snang srid sems su shes pa na //
NK103(pe)019:803: dbang po yan par bzhag kyang rang byung ye shes gsal //
NK103(pe)019:804: snying po don gyi rang bzhin la //
NK103(pe)019:805: blos ci yang mi bsgom phyogs ris gang yang man //
NK103(pe)019:806: khyu mchog glang po che btul ba'i sems ltar ma bcos pa //
NK103(pe)019:807: rang bzhag rig pa'i 'khor lo nyid la dus gsum
NK103(pe)019:808: gang du'ang ting nge la btang ba dang bzhag pa
NK103(pe)019:809: med // yul gang yang mi 'dzin pas ci yang bkag pa med //
NK103(pe)019:810: snying po don gyi rang bzhin la //
NK103(pe)019:811: skyon dang yon tan gnyis med pas //
NK103(pe)019:812: rdzogs pa'i lta ba blang dor med //
NK103(pe)019:813: dmigs pa 'jug tu med ting 'dzin las ma yengs pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:814: 'od gsal rig pa'i sems nyid yin /
NK103(pe)019:815: rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung thugs kyi ma bcos pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:816: rnam dag rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs //
NK103(pe)019:817: btsal med snying po don la bzhag pa las 'byung ngo //
NK103(pe)019:818: byang chub sems kyi don nyid la //
NK103(pe)019:819: nges pa'i theg pa gcig ste de ni snying po'i don no //
NK103(pe)019:820: rang rang gi bsam pa dang mthun pa'i theg pa sna tshogs pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:821: drang ba'i don nyid du 'gyur gyi nges pa'i don min //
NK103(pe)019:822: ngo bo nyid chos nyid la theg pa mthon dman
NK103(pe)019:823: med mos pa tha dad 'jug pa'i bsam pas mthon
NK103(pe)019:824: dman rtog pas brtags par zad lang+kara gshegs pa las
NK103(pe)019:826: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK103(pe)019:827: sems ni yongs su gyur pa na //
NK103(pe)019:828: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK103(pe)019:829: ces gsungs pa dang mthun no //
NK103(pe)019:830: sems nyid nyag gcig phyogs bral la //
NK103(pe)019:831: theg pa du ma'i 'bras bu med la lam yang du ma min //
NK103(pe)019:832: ma bcos rnal 'byor rdzogs pa chen po'i lam la
NK103(pe)019:833: ni tha dad mi gnas te thams cad lam gyi
NK103(pe)019:835: de yang sa lam ma bgrod kyang mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i lam 'di nyid ni /
NK103(pe)019:836: dang po skyed pa'i rgyu rkyen med pas tha ma'ang skye 'jig med de //
NK103(pe)019:837: gdod nas rang byung snying por gsal //
NK103(pe)019:838: ris drug ji ltar snang ba dang //
NK103(pe)019:839: mya ngan 'das pa'i rang bzhin la tha dad du
NK103(pe)019:840: 'dzin kyang don la dbyer med rang byung sems su
NK103(pe)019:841: gcig / rigs drug sems kyi rtog pa dang //
NK103(pe)019:842: ye shes rang gsal rig pa nyid //
NK103(pe)019:843: khyad par med de snying por gcig kyang gnyis su snang ba ni //
NK103(pe)019:844: khams gsum 'khor ba'i snang ba 'khrul pa dang //
NK103(pe)019:845: mya ngan 'das pa'i ye shes ma 'khrul ba 0nyid //
NK103(pe)019:846: rtogs 0ma rtogs kyis gnyis su byung //
NK103(pe)019:847: rtogs pas rang sems nyid la thug pas //
NK103(pe)019:848: gzhan nas 'dod cing re ba'i rtsol ba bral //
NK103(pe)019:849: rang sems rnam dag ni ye sangs rgyas te kun bzang rgyal ba'i sems nyid du bde //
NK103(pe)019:850: mtha' yas 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK103(pe)019:851: rgyal ba'i ye shes rang chas su ldan te //
NK103(pe)019:852: bsam bral rang lugs cir yang mi dgongs so //
NK103(pe)019:853: ye shes nam mkha'i mtha' lta bur cir yang //
NK103(pe)019:854: yid la mi byed de yid kyi bya ba btang //
NK103(pe)019:855: rang la 'khor ba mya ngan 'das pa yi //
NK103(pe)019:856: rnam rtog phra rags cir snang yang //
NK103(pe)019:857: rang lugs su bzhag pas bsam bral nyid du bde //
NK103(pe)019:858: chu yi snang ba thams cad rlan par gcig pa ji bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:859: phra rags kyi rnam rtog ye shes nyid du ro gcig /
NK103(pe)019:861: 'khor bar gnas kyang gdod nas dag /
NK103(pe)019:862: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa cir byung yang brtags na chu shing lta bur snying po med //
NK103(pe)019:863: ma rig thibs po'i 'khor ba na //
NK103(pe)019:864: rig pa mar me'i snying po lta bur gsal //
NK103(pe)019:865: rnam par rtog pa cir 'gyur yang //
NK103(pe)019:866: rang rig gnyug ma ni rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad kyang //
NK103(pe)019:867: nyi ma la gsal 'grib med par nam langs na
NK103(pe)019:868: gsal bar 'dzin pa'i sems dang nub kha na mi
NK103(pe)019:870: ye shes kyi don la gsal 'grib med kyang rtogs
NK103(pe)019:871: na gsal ma rtogs na mi gsal ba de bzhin
NK103(pe)019:872: no // ma bsgrubs par ye shes rang gsal ngang gis 'byung ngo //
NK103(pe)019:873: skal ldan ma bcos rnal 'byor pas //
NK103(pe)019:874: sems nyid lteng ka'i chu mi g.yo ba ltar du gnas na //
NK103(pe)019:875: lus ngag gi rtsol ba ngang gis zhi //
NK103(pe)019:876: bde ba'i ye shes mi rtog pa //
NK103(pe)019:877: shes rab gsal ba'i snying po 'di //
NK103(pe)019:878: mthar phyin na rang byung gi ye shes mi rtog pa'i ngo bor gyur pa'o //
NK103(pe)019:879: dran med sgyu ma ye shes gsal te //
NK103(pe)019:880: rang gnas 'gro ba yongs la khyab //
NK103(pe)019:881: nam mkha' lta bur dbyer med pa'i gnas lugs 'gro ba'i sems las gzhan na med //
NK103(pe)019:882: rtog med ngang las shar ba yi //
NK103(pe)019:883: rig pa bde ba'i mtshan nyid can //
NK103(pe)019:884: 'dzin pa 'khrul pa dag byed ye shes ni //
NK103(pe)019:885: ma bcos par bzhag na ngang gis rang rig gsal //
NK103(pe)019:886: bde ba'i rang rig rtog pa bral //
NK103(pe)019:887: rang gnas ye shes 'od gsal byang chub sems nyid de //
NK103(pe)019:888: mthong bas the tshom rgyu ba bral //
NK103(pe)019:889: ye shes rang la gdod nas gnas pas glo bur gyi rtog pas sgrib pa med //
NK103(pe)019:890: chos thams cad ye shes su gsal bar mthong bas //
NK103(pe)019:891: snying po'i don la gzhan du gol sa med //
NK103(pe)019:893: rtsol bral rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung ye shes
NK103(pe)019:894: yin la rang byung ye shes ni chos kun gyi
NK103(pe)019:895: bdag nyid de // de la lus dang bral bas yan lag med //
NK103(pe)019:896: de nyid sgro skur kun dang bral ba'i dngos gzhi can //
NK103(pe)019:897: snying po'i don ni mtha' kun bral yang chos kun
NK103(pe)019:898: gyi bdag nyid las ma bcos ni rig pa'i ting
NK103(pe)019:900: rtsol ba'i bya ba med bzhin du rang gzhan gyi don kun rdzogs so //
NK103(pe)019:901: rang byung ye shes ma bcos gnyug ma byang chub
NK103(pe)019:902: kyi sems ni 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi gzhi
NK103(pe)019:903: // sa bgrod du med kyang 'khrul pa las rnam
NK103(pe)019:904: par grol te yon tan lhun gyis grub pa ni
NK103(pe)019:905: // lam // gnas lugs ji bzhin pa che ba'i yon tan kun rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu nyid //
NK103(pe)019:906: de gsum ka thig le chen po'i klong du dbyer med pas gzhi lam 'bras bu gcig gi ngang //
NK103(pe)019:907: sems nyid la rtsol ba'i bya ba dang bral ba la yon tan rdzogs pa'i gter //
NK103(pe)019:908: bde ba'i ye shes cir yang mi rtog ste rgyal ba'i thugs de //
NK103(pe)019:909: skal ldan la dang po nyid nas rdzogs par 'chad //
NK103(pe)019:911: rgyal ba'i ye shes mya ngan las 'das par //
NK103(pe)019:912: bde chen rig par gcig gi ngang //
NK103(pe)019:913: rang byung ma bcos ji bzhin pa ni //
NK103(pe)019:914: yon tan lhun rdzogs spros pa med pa'i ngang //
NK103(pe)019:915: blos bsam du med pa'i ye shes 'di //
NK103(pe)019:916: rnam par rtog pa'i rgyu ba bral te dus gsum mi mnga' yang rgyun mi 'chad do //
NK103(pe)019:917: sems nyid sgrub pa'i lam mchog 'di //
NK103(pe)019:918: slob dpon nyid dang dbyer med par 'gro ba kun la ldan bzhin du //
NK103(pe)019:919: snang ba'i 'od kyi lam med pas 'khor bar 'khyams
NK103(pe)019:920: te zhen drug sdug bsngal gsum mam brgyad dang theg
NK103(pe)019:921: brgyad rtsol ba'i nad kyis gdungs //
NK103(pe)019:922: des na snying po gnas lugs kyi don gsal bar byed pa'i sgron ma 'od 'di //
NK103(pe)019:923: phyi rabs rnal 'byor rnams kyi don du //
NK103(pe)019:924: gang ltar na bla ma kha'phags pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK103(pe)019:926: gang gis bdag gis ka rtogs //
NK103(pe)019:927: snying rjes kun nas bslang ste brtsams pa'i dge ba yongs la bsngo //
NK103(pe)019:928: snying po de kho na nyid rin po che 'od ces bya ba'i sgrub thabs /
NK103(pe)019:929: yang dag pa'i sa la gnas pa'i slob dpon sh+r+ai sing+hasa mdzad pa /
NK103(pe)019:930: rdzogs so////rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh+r+ai sing+ha pra b+ha ta dang /
NK103(pe)019:931: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong bee ro tsa
NK103(pe)019:932: nas yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang du bsgyur cing
NK103(pe)019:933: zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
